{"tid":354661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本表明若北韓導彈飛越上空 可行使集體自衛權","createTime":"2017-08-10T15:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T17:05:53.000Z","uid":4783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"027c67eea11724a6c50f287551ec0c826b0c260c","tid":354661,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】北韓聲言研究向關島附近海域，發射中程彈道導彈。日本防衛相小野寺五典在國會表明，一旦北韓發射導彈飛越日本上空，日本確認為「存亡危機事態」，就能夠行使集體自衛權。<br />\n<br />\n小野寺五典出席眾議院安全保障委員會指出，「美國對事態缺乏遏制力的話，日本有可能面臨相當於存亡的危機」。小野寺五典又說，日本自衛隊的神盾級戰艦，可以攔截導彈。<br />\n<br />\n日本官房長官菅義偉在記者會上表示，「這是對包含日本在內的地區及國際社會之安全保障的明顯挑釁行為，日本絕對不能允許」。<br />\n<br />\n日本2015年通過法案，允許行使集體自衛權。若與日本有密切關係的第三國遭到武力攻擊時，經認定屬於有讓日本的存亡遭受威脅的明顯危險之「存亡危機事態」之下，即可使用集體自衛權。<br />\n<br />\nsource：星島<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/480117-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%8B%A5%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E9%A3%9B%E8%B6%8A%E4%B8%8A%E7%A9%BA+%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E6%AC%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F480117-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25A9%25BA%2B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%25AC%258A&d=UNUPZMWQpYrXbJpK9qmRxr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=61021e6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F480117-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25B6%258A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25A9%25BA%2B%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%259B%25E6%25AC%258A&h=3f3a0567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/480117-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%8B%A5%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88%E9%A3%9B%E8%B6%8A%E4%B8%8A%E7%A9%BA+%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%9B%E6%AC%8A</a>"},{"pid":"375ca4d46a4bb74085fba985304baf774cc8d690","tid":354661,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"9up"},{"pid":"294c2915259fe4019b890f21cde11ac9219e64ee","tid":354661,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"東亞國家一向都係打咀炮多<br />\n<br />\n北韓, 南韓, 日本, 台灣, 中共<br />\n大家講開戰講左30幾年, 但一槍都未開過"},{"pid":"563efb7b0e388c97d5c9d11064743c297983f59e","tid":354661,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"北泡向東射啦，射落海唔好玩"},{"pid":"b14ee2354e85883c025aea24e7aac823c7f2f022","tid":354661,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北泡向東射遠啲啦，射落海唔好玩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"084efac20de96c4f671cffe28240380bfe2ac0c8","tid":354661,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東亞國家一向都係打咀炮多<br />\n<br />\n北韓, 南韓, 日本, 台灣, 中共<br />\n大家講開戰講左30幾年, 但一槍都未開過</blockquote><br />\n北韓同南韓隔幾年就打吓火炮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38a49ff1ed13956356009a7af5104b1d6802c12","tid":354661,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東亞國家一向都係打咀炮多<br />\n<br />\n北韓, 南韓, 日本, 台灣, 中共<br />\n大家講開戰講左30幾年, 但一槍都未開過</blockquote><br />\n開過好多槍wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}